name: sato
_description: Do this on a GBKOW RA. Will produce a lvl 99 mag with 5 DEF, 49 POW, 45 DEX, and 0 MIND. Hand it to a VBRW Female FO and feed it 3 more monomates. Will evolve into lvl 100 Sato with stats 5|50|45|0.
_usage_instructions: rename this file to mags.json and run the .exe in the same directory.
